claimant that either (i) does not reside with his spouse during the
taxable year, or (ii) resides with his spouse during the taxable year and
only one (1) of them is sixty-five (65) years of age or older at the end
of the taxable year, shall be determined in accordance with the
following schedule:</span></p>
